<plot>Duda (Stulbach), a business man who is about to receive a fortune that'll allow him to open new factories, decides to live a straight life, breaking up with his lover and becoming an honest man. However, in his last date with the lover, his cell phone accidentaly dials his wife's number - and she starts to listening everything that is happening through her car's speaker phone. Meanwhile, Duda's partner is trying to steal all his money and two inexperienced thieves are going to complicate the situation even more by kidnapping Duda and his lover.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?642242</url></doc>
